      "Custom cabinetry design",
      "Appliance integration",
      "Plumbing and electrical layout",
      "Tile and countertop selection",
      "Storage optimization",
      "Professional installation",
    ],
    price: "From ₹6,60,000",
    duration: "per space",
    isPopular: false,
  },
  {
    title: "Commercial Interior Design",
    description:
      "Professional interior design for offices, retail spaces, and commercial properties.",
    icon: '<svg fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 7V3H2v18h20V7H12zM6 19H4v-2h2v2zm0-4H4v-2h2v2zm0-4H4V9h2v2zm0-4H4V5h2v2zm4 12H8v-2h2v2zm0-4H8v-2h2v2zm0-4H8V9h2v2zm0-4H8V5h2v2zm10 12h-8v-2h2v-2h-2v-2h2v-2h-2V9h8v10z"/></svg>',
    features: [
      "Space planning and layout",
      "Brand integration",
      "Ergonomic furniture selection",
      "Lighting and acoustics",
      "Compliance and safety standards",
      "Project coordination",
    ],
    price: "From ₹12,40,000",
    duration: "per project",
    isPopular: false,
  },
  {
    title: "Renovation & Remodeling",
    description:
      "Complete renovation services with design expertise and construction management.",
    icon: '<svg fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M22.7 19l-9.1-9.1c.9-2.3.4-5-1.5-6.9-2-2-5-2.4-7.4-1.3L9 6 6 9 1.6 4.7C.4 7.1.9 10.1 2.9 12.1c1.9 1.9 4.6 2.4 6.9 1.5l9.1 9.1c.4.4 1 .4 1.4 0l2.3-2.3c.5-.4.5-1.1.1-1.4z"/></svg>',
